data.description: Beautiful Far Eastside home available May 6th! This corner property has 3 bedrooms, 2 baths and a built in Surround Sound! Solar Panels, a FIREPLACE  to keep cozy in the winter and REFRIGERATED AIR to stay cool in the summer! Full appliance package to include washer and dryer. Large tile throughout the property, NO CARPET! Epoxy-coated garage flooring with overhead storage and builtin cabinets for extra storage.  Nice Desert landscaping in the front and backyard, front yard has lights and the backyard also has a small pergola. Park in walking distance. Schedule your showing today!!
